@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@token = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### 로그인
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@graphify.dev",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### GET /users/me — 성공
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET /users/me — 실패 (미인증)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me

###

### PUT /users/me/password — 성공
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "password1234"
}

###

### PUT /users/me/password — 실패 (현재 비밀번호 불일치)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "wrong",
  "newPassword": "password1234"
}

###

### PUT /users/me/prompt — 성공 (Premium)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/prompt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customPrompt": "HBM 공급망 분석 시 투자 관계를 우선 요약해 주세요."
}

###

### POST /auth/logout — 성공
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
